text: Toto is a given name which may refer to: * Toto of Nepi (died 768), Roman duke * Toto Landero (born 1995), Filipino boxer * Toto Makgolokwe (died 1927), paramount chief of the Batlharo tribe of South Africa * Toto Mwandjani, Malagasy guitarist * Toto Sena Govou (born 1989), French-Beninese footballer * Toto Tamuz (born 1988), Nigerian-born Israeli footballer * Toto Wong (born 1999), Hong Kong swimmer ==See also== *Tono (name)
title: Toto (given name)
